introduction: Urzila's unique blend of wit and charm has resonated with audiences worldwide. Her NETFLIX hour-long comedy special Overqualified Loser, released in 190 countries, and its companion piece, Comedians of the World, testify to her universal appeal and comedic genius. Urzila toured throughout Australia, New Zealand, Canada, and Europe to sold-out crowds with her show, It’s Personal, which was filmed earlier in the year at the Brisbane Powerhouse.In 2024, Urzila is poised to make her mark in feature films by lending her voice to Honkus in the animated film Ozi. This exciting project boasts a star-studded cast, including Donald Sutherland, Laura Dern and Amandla Stenberg. Urzila has also been cast in the Netflix and Happy Madison’s rom-com Kinda Pregnant, alongside Amy Schumer.
